        "management": "Intensive topical antibiotics: Fortified Cefazolin 5% + Gentamicin 1.4% hourly alternating. or Monotherapy: Moxifloxacin 0.5% hourly. Cycloplegics. Scraping for culture. Consider systemic if severe."
